为什么人们会分享 Sydney Sweeney 的“Hot Ones”表情包？ https://www.nme.com/news/film/why-are-people-sharing-the-sydney-sweeney-hot-ones-meme-3578824?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=why-are-people-sharing-悉尼理发师 - Hot-ones-memeAlex Berry Mon, 29 Jan 2024 22:00:09 +0000 Film NewsNewsEuphoria https://www.nme.com/?p=3578824 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Sydney-Sweeney-meme.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="悉尼·斯威尼 Meme" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Sydney-Sweeney-meme.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Sydney-Sweeney-meme-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Sydney-Sweeney-meme-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Sydney-Sweeney-meme-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Sydney-Sweeney-meme-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Sydney-Sweeney-meme-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这张截图在她“Hot Ones”亮相后迅速走红</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/why-are-people-sharing-the-sydney-sweeney-hot-ones-meme-3578824">为什么人们会分享 Sydney Sweeney 的“Hot Ones”模因？</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Sydney-Sweeney-meme.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="悉尼·斯威尼 Meme" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Sydney-Sweeney-meme.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Sydney-Sweeney-meme-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Sydney-Sweeney-meme-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Sydney-Sweeney-meme-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Sydney-Sweeney-meme-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Sydney-Sweeney-meme-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>西德尼·斯威尼 (Sydney Sweeney) 在<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=a9ZhleGV4Qc" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《Hot Ones</em></a> 》中的亮相走红后，成为了社交媒体上流传的最新表情包的代言人。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/euphoria-season-2-review-zendaya-hbo-3132916">《幸福感》第二季评论：仍然是电视上最好的青少年电视剧</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/euphoria"><em>《幸福感》</em></a>明星一直在宣传她即将上映的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/marvel">漫威</a>电影《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/dakota-johnson-says-filming-on-madame-web-was-absolutely-psychotic-3574495"><em>韦伯夫人》</em></a> ，她出现在肖恩·埃文斯主持的 YouTube 系列<em>《Hot Ones》</em>的最新一集中。</p><p>该系列节目中，名人一边回答问题，一边吃着不同辣度酱汁的鸡翅，每一轮的辣度都会增加。</p><p>该视频自上周上传以来已获得 270 万次观看，其缩略图已成为社交媒体上流传的一个梗。</p><h2><strong>悉尼斯威尼模因从何而来？</strong></h2><p>该表情包是一张斯威尼满怀渴望地抬起头、笑容满面的照片。这张截图是她在 YouTube 热播系列节目<em>《Hot Ones》</em>中亮相的截图，她将其发布在自己的 Instagram 页面上，并配上标题“这是为男孩们做的”。</p><p>这段视频的标题是<em>《西德尼·斯威尼一边吃辣</em><em>鸡翅</em>一边忍受噩梦》，这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_asia/news/film/sydney-sweeney-anyone-but-you-is-biggest-romcom-bridget-jones-baby-3575210"><em>除了你之外的任何人都</em></a>成功完成了每一轮挑战。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C2lGjlNPp5s/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px;